  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Munchy Mammals</strong> is a tricky puzzle game about strategy, snacking, and survival. Guide adorable animals of various lengths as they munch on fruit—and sometimes each other—to squeeze into their hiding spots!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/00fef9f7c25f9cd2940a700bd431435a.poster.avif?t=1758552547\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/00fef9f7c25f9cd2940a700bd431435a.webm?t=1758552547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/00fef9f7c25f9cd2940a700bd431435a.mp4?t=1758552547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the player, you'll need to plan their moves carefully. Each mammal has unique skills and diets, from gentle herbivores to meat-loving carnivores, adding a delicious twist to every puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/de73fc864b123a6ff884c74f242b2d0c.poster.avif?t=1758552547\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/de73fc864b123a6ff884c74f242b2d0c.webm?t=1758552547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/de73fc864b123a6ff884c74f242b2d0c.mp4?t=1758552547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With over 60 challenging levels, evolving creatures, and a level editor for endless new challenges, <strong>Munchy Mammals</strong> will keep you thinking and munching. Ready to outsmart the food chain? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/c2ed3b7843321160454c079527f48070.poster.avif?t=1758552547\" width=600 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/c2ed3b7843321160454c079527f48070.webm?t=1758552547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/c2ed3b7843321160454c079527f48070.mp4?t=1758552547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think you’ve mastered all 60+ levels? Test your skills with endless player-made puzzles, and collect more gold medals than any muncher before! With fresh levels added regularly, the challenges never end.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity and design your own levels to share with the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/e4659ca52eb44ed1ff9b9d1b1411b3b1.poster.avif?t=1758552547\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/e4659ca52eb44ed1ff9b9d1b1411b3b1.webm?t=1758552547\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382920/extras/e4659ca52eb44ed1ff9b9d1b1411b3b1.mp4?t=1758552547\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 60+ mind-bending puzzles with increasing difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different areas with unique art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist design; no keys, boxes, or doors to distract from the puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move tracker & medals for the perfectionists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully-featured Level Editor to create and share your own puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless new levels from players around the world in the level browser</p></li></ul>",
