ass=\"bb_paragraph\" >Minimalist design; no keys, boxes, or doors to distract from the puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move tracker & medals for the perfectionists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully-featured Level Editor to create and share your own puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless new levels from players around the world in the level browser</p></li></ul>",
